lead_paragraph: A picture on Nov. 15 with a Sports of The Times column, about Andre Agassi’s recent tour to promote his new memoir, “Open,” carried an erroneous credit in some editions. The photograph showing Agassi and his collaborator on the book, J. R. Moehringer, was by Isaac Brekken for The New York Times, not by Stuart Isett for The New York Times.
